project_descr:
"Dialogue Mechanism-Phase 2"
Objective: to create and preserve an enabling environment for ongoing open dialogue and direct engagement between Georgian Government and Abkhaz de-facto authorities.

outputs.output_descr: Complementary to other multi-party dialogue platforms, incl. the Geneva International Discussions (GID), and operating independently of political challenges, the Dialogue project provides a reliable means of direct collaboration across the dividing line.
